afford to pay your rent?

401
00:35:50,262 --> 00:35:53,509
- It seemed like a great buy at the time.

402
00:35:53,510 --> 00:35:54,879
- You've gotta be more responsible

403
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,880
