Cut off all his toes.

440
00:40:56,599 --> 00:41:00,589
Nasty.

441
00:41:00,590 --> 00:41:01,590
Very nasty.

442
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:04,803
- What a horrible way to die.

443
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:07,759
